15
00:01:11,950 --> 00:01:20,369
The money required to cover the costs is
called revenues, which mainly come from

16
00:01:20,369 --> 00:01:27,909
public sources. Public financing systems
have two main downsides. On the one hand,

17
00:01:27,909 --> 00:01:33,170
they are vulnerable to political factors
and national economic problems. In

18
00:01:33,170 --> 00:01:38,539
