and the affordability of the citizens. In

80
00:06:48,650 --> 00:06:50,420
the case of not willing to pay,

81
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:54,350
collecting direct user charges may
require an efficient enforcement

82
00:06:54,350 --> 00:06:59,240
mechanism. It is difficult to just stop
the service for those that do not pay,

83
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:03,440
because then they litter and that would
affect all the others who are paying.

84
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:08,940
This is the aspect of a public good,
we're all affected if one does not

85
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:13,510
comply. Combining bills with other 
utility bills allows to make effective

86
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:18,280
sanctions in the case of non-payment.
Linking waste fee collection to

87
